OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight fog and low cloud
OL,6,Fdispersing this morning, although some
OL,7,Fmay linger across Harris, Lewis and
OL,8,Fthe Sutherland coast. Otherwise dry
OL,9,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Warm, and
OL,10,Flocally very warm in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will be dry and clear with
OL,15,Fsome patchy fog and low cloud. Patchy
OL,16,Ffrost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FDry in the morning with some
OL,19,Fsunshine. Clouding over in the
OL,20,Fafternoon with the chance of the of a
OL,21,Ffew showers later. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
