OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCooler
OL,6,Fand cloudy over the weekend with a
OL,7,Fchance of showers, these most
OL,8,Fwidespread on Saturday. Rain at first
OL,9,Fon Monday then mainly dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
